     Using The Vault:  To deposit items into the Vault, View a character's
     items, highlight the desired item and use the Deposit command.  To
     deposit specific amount of money, View the character, highlight the
     appropriate denomination and use the Deposit command.  To deposit all
     of the party's money choose the Pool command.


     Combat Commands
     ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
         ESC: Will 'take back' a move.  The function will not erase any damage
              taken during the move.

       ALT/Q: Sets all characters to QUICK (computer control).

     <SPACE>: Returns all character to normal control from QUICK.

       ALT/M: Toggles the magic spells on/off of for characters set to QUICK

     CNTRL/S: Toggles sound on/off (may be used any time).

        HINT: If you find combat too easy or difficult, use the ALTER and LEVEL
              command.

